 205

 208

 210         entries only present in the current lockfile; the second, `inthat`,
 211         contains entries only present in the given one.
 212

 214         is present in both dicts, pointing to values from each file.
 215         """
 216         diff_data = {
 217             "default": SectionDifference({}, {}),
 218             "develop": SectionDifference({}, {}),
 219         }
 220         for section_name, section_diff in diff_data.items():
 221             try:
 222                 this = self.lockfile[section_name]._data
 223             except (KeyError, TypeError):
 224                 this = {}

 226                 that = lockfile[section_name]._data
 227             except (KeyError, TypeError):
 228                 that = {}

 230                 try:
 231                     that_value = that[key]
